text: Diggah nanu tama munaafiqhiinil mariiy mara siinik Qiday, hinnay sinni dabooqak eweqa iyyaanam keenil nuktubeh Suginninoy woh abak manannon keenik dago mara akke waytek, Diggah usun Yallaa kee kay farmoytih amriy ken kassiisaanaah ken kah amrisaana abinnoonuy Addunyaay Akeeral galtoh keenih aysuk ten, ken lubbittet iimaan diggaa kee kay arcisiyyah keenih aysuk ten
